nh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A0nh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-_3Q8NyAr4CRqKgdIYAsADA">Thành thượng - 城上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-kh%C3%A1ch-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-DDdgPU469woqng0TncYD8A">Thu nhật khách trung tác - 秋日客中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-dW12UVYh-vPxg4IlKpEmEA">Tích biệt hành, tống Lưu bộc xạ phán quan - 惜別行送劉僕射判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/T%C3%B9ng-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-V%C3%A2n-qu%C3%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch-%E1%BB%A9ng-gi%C3%A1o/poem-QVWcxWXDqNDdc9vG5Oon9A">Tùng quốc công Đồng Vân quán đề bích ứng giáo - 從國公彤雲舘題壁應教</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6qvbBFPqKGw1jJEFfSUB_Q">Xuân nguyên hữu cảm kỳ 1 - 春元有感其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
